---
title: Easy Celtic-Style Chicken & Gravy Burger with Lemon Pepper Roasted Spuds & Slaw
description: Gather around the table to get a bite at this chicken burger slathered in gravy. Make it an occasion and invite some friends to join
the team spirit. Everyone will love the peppery lemon roasted spud slices. We’re sure you’ll be this burger’s biggest fan.
